snippet.title: RCLifeOn
snippet.description: My name is Simon Sörensen and I am the creator of RCLifeOn. I do a little bit of everything, nothing too fancy. I love 3D printing, DIY and radio controlled stuff. Yeah, that's pretty much it. If you want to be a part of my family here on YouTube, hit the subscribe button and let's hang out!
